strings: <voice_0x01000E58><se_def>*: It is very dangerous to continue hunting demons. Let's see what we've done with Golden...
<voice_0x01000E59><se_def>*: Exercise "Who are you, who are you?"
<voice_0x01000E5A><se_def>*: Interesting... I thought there was no one on the island. Except us and the man who killed Goldin.
<voice_0x01000E5B><se_def>*: I want to give some advice. Visit the ancient ruins in the central part of the island.
<voice_0x01000E5C><se_def>*: Ignore it as it's very dangerous! you have been warned.
